## 🛠️ Prerequisites

Before you start, you need these installed on your computer:

*   **Node.js (v20+)**: [Download here](https://nodejs.org/)
*   **Docker**: [Download Desktop](https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/) (Required for the database and worker)
